          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1641914789487-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), the<strong> lemon zest</strong>, the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> haddock bites </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this your <strong>gremolata fish</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1641914820256-x200.jpg",
