    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish cakes are cooking, top, tail and chop the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into quarters lengthways, then into batons</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into thin wedges</p>",
